<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4423816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663855" alt="Dr_Naxurt" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4423816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;">Dr_Naxurt</a></span></p>
